#!/usr/bin/env python3
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
#
# SConstruct  (Madagascar Script)
#
# Purpose: Obtain zero offset CRS parameters using VFSA.
# for a set of (t0,m0) pairs.
#
# Site: https://dirack.github.io
# 
# Version 1.0
#
# Programmer: Rodolfo A. C. Neves (Dirack) 13/08/2021
